title: Brent Weinbach
description: Brent Weinbach (Conan! The Legacy Music Hour podcast!) is hands down one of the weirdest guests we've ever had. Pete felt conflicted about this conversation for DAYS after recording it because how do you navigate a person like Brent?! Holy cow. He out weirded our weirdest weirdness in a hilarious and fun way. Great ep, great guest, WEIRD TIMES WITH PAT HALMS.
